{"title_page": "Frank McGurk (boxer)", "text_new": "{{short description|British boxer}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2020}}\n{{Infobox sportsperson\n| name           = Frank McGurk\n| full_name      = \n| image          = \n| caption        = \n| nationality    = British\n| sport          = [[Boxing]]\n| birth_date     = {{birth date|df=yes|1880|9|8}}\n| birth_place    = [[Glasgow]], Scotland\n| death_date     = \n| death_place    = \n}}\n\n'''Frank McGurk''' (born 8 September 1880, date of death unknown) was a British [[boxing|boxer]]. He competed in the [[Boxing at the 1908 Summer Olympics \u2013 Bantamweight|men's bantamweight]] event at the [[1908 Summer Olympics]].<ref name=\"SportsRef\">{{cite Sports-Reference |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/mc/frank-mcgurk-1.html |title=Frank McGurk Olympic Results |accessdate=4 November 2018}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:McGurk, Frank}}\n[[Category:1880 births]]\n[[Category:Year of death missing]]\n[[Category:Scottish male boxers]]\n[[Category:British male boxers]]\n[[Category:Olympic boxers of Great Britain]]\n[[Category:Boxers at the 1908 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Glasgow]]\n{{UK-boxing-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|British boxer}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=November 2018}}\n{{Infobox sportsperson\n| name           = Frank McGurk\n| full_name      = \n| image          = \n| caption        = \n| nationality    = British\n| sport          = [[Boxing]]\n| birth_date     = {{birth date|1880|9|8}}\n| birth_place    = [[Glasgow]], Scotland\n| death_date     = \n| death_place    = \n}}\n\n'''Frank McGurk''' (born 8 September 1880, date of death unknown) was a British [[boxing|boxer]]. He competed in the [[Boxing at the 1908 Summer Olympics \u2013 Bantamweight|men's bantamweight]] event at the [[1908 Summer Olympics]].<ref name=\"SportsRef\">{{cite Sports-Reference |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/mc/